-size:12pt">ed the authorities and a cessation of works was issued in the December</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> 2011</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">. After 7 months of inaction I was advised by my local authority to follow the Highways Act 1980. In October 2012  I phoned the Local Government Ombudsman for advice.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">I was advised </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">to follow the complaints procedure through my local authority and if the issue was not resolved or I was not happy with the outcome then I could make an official complaint to the Ombudsman.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-indent:36pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Listed below are the results of this procedure.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">1.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:7pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:7pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:7pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:7pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:7pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:7pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">17-10-12. Stage 1 complaint</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">2.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:7pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:7pt